name: TweetLibs
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tweet libs
des:
Play simple mad libs over and over again using your Alexa devices. You can select the category of mad lib you would like such as "Actors", "Food", "Athletes", and more! Then Alexa will request the information it needs to complete the mad lib.

Once you've finished giving all the information it needs, it will tell you the final mad lib and will also tweet out the results from https://twitter.com/alexatweetlibs so you can see all the mad libs that everyone plays around the world.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
